SIMPLE: dealing
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dealing
<hw>Deal"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of one who deals;
distribution of anything, as of cards to the players; method of
business; traffic; intercourse; transaction; <as>as, to have
<ex>dealings</ex> with a person</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Double dealing</b></col>, <cd>insincere, treacherous
dealing; duplicity.</cd> -- <col><b>Plain dealing</b></col>, <cd>fair,
sincere, honorable dealing; honest, outspoken expression of
opinion.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dealth</ent>⟦br⟧
